
Spring MVC Controller
---------------------
	Spring MVC REST API
		- recieves request URI
		- maps the uri + HTTP method to a functionality (Java Method)
		- returns a response in JSON format
		
	Course API
		Resources - are the things in your domain
			- Topic, Course, Lesson
				- Topic can have multiple Courses and a Course can have multiple Lessons
				
		GET 	/topics			Get all topics
		GET		/topics/id		Get the particular topic
		POST	/topics			Create new topic
		PUT		/topics/id		Update the particular topic
		DELETE	/topics/id		Delete the particular topic
